\begin_layout Standard
We would like a session continuation mechanism to replace cookies that has
 better security semantics.
 In particular we would like a system that uses cryptographic algorithms
 and cryptographic session keys, and is amenable to being keyed by HTTP
 and web authentication mechanisms, is suitable for use in web and non-web
 HTTP applications, and can be keyed even for unauthenticated sessions.
\end_layout

